Originally the larger, older guilds (I hate the term uber...only applies to BotS anyways) wanted more chances at epic loot to complete their quests faster. Then it turned into &quot;we have too many posting entities&quot;, I can agree with that. Now it's &quot;BB guilds need more days&quot;, I won't agree with that. If you wanna base it on numbers then do so and give ANY entity with 75 or more planeable toons an extra day.<br>
<br>
